ZH: 我们需要一笔贷款，所以我们把房子抵押了。
EN: We needed a loan, so we mortgaged our house.

ZH: 他们把车抵押给了银行以换取资金。
EN: They mortgaged their car to the bank in exchange for funds.

ZH: 这家公司把机器设备抵押给了投资者。
EN: This company mortgaged its machinery to investors.

ZH: 他们通过抵押把土地变现了。
EN: They liquidated their land through mortgaging.

ZH: 我们可以用抵押的方式来获取资金。
EN: We can obtain funds through mortgaging.

ZH: 这是一种常见的抵押方式。
EN: This is a common way of mortgaging.

ZH: 我们需要一些抵押品来获得贷款。
EN: We need some collateral to secure a loan.

ZH: 他们用房屋作为抵押品获得了大笔资金。
EN: They used their house as collateral to obtain a large sum of money.

ZH: 他们已经把贵重物品抵押给了银行。
EN: They have already mortgaged valuable items to the bank.

ZH: 他们的所有资产都被抵押了。
EN: All of their assets have been mortgaged.

ZH: 我们没有任何东西可以抵押。
EN: We have nothing to mortgage.

ZH: 他们通过抵押来偿还了债务。
EN: They repaid their debt through mortgaging.

ZH: 抵押可能会带来风险。
EN: Mortgaging can come with risks.

ZH: 银行接受房产、车辆等财产作为抵押。
EN: Banks accept properties like houses and vehicles as collateral.

ZH: 抵押品的价值必须高于所借资金。
EN: The value of the collateral must be higher than the borrowed funds.

ZH: 这种贷款需要抵押品作为担保。
EN: This loan requires collateral as security.

ZH: 他们不得不抵押土地来支付医疗费用。
EN: They had to mortgage their land to pay for medical expenses.

ZH: 这笔交易中没有抵押品的价值。
EN: There is no value in the collateral in this transaction.

ZH: 抵押品可以是任何具有价值的东西。
EN: Collateral can be anything of value.

ZH: 银行会审查抵押品的价值。
EN: The bank will review the value of the collateral.
